## 批量导入

importFile.js

```js
// 接受一个正则的参数，默认匹配去除该后缀
const importAll = (reg = /\.vue$/g) => {
  return context => {
    const map = {}
    for (const key of context.keys()) {
      const keyArr = key.split('/')
      keyArr.shift() // 移除.
      map[keyArr.join('.').replace(reg, '')] = context(key)
    }
  
    return map
  }
}

export default importAll
```

使用

```js
import importFun from '@/utils/importFile'
const importVue = importFun(/\.vue$/g) // 利用柯里化先生成引入函数
console.log('importFun', importVue(require.context('./components/form', true, /\.vue$/)))
```

> ```js
> require.context(directory, useSubdirectories, regExp)
> ```
> 
> directory: 要查找的文件路径
> useSubdirectories: 是否查找子目录
> regExp: 要匹配文件的正则
